{"id":232973671,"title":"真麻煩啊 失戀","content":"如題 昨天分手了 我提的 \n我喜歡對方 但感覺對方不喜歡了 所以成全他\n最後提完 對方已讀不回後 就邁入失戀階段了\n以前也失戀過 只能靠時間治癒\n可能是太有經驗😭 比較不會像以前哭到無法下床\n或是半夜無法入睡 要靠安眠藥或酒精 \n但還是會時間到就忍不住流眼淚 \n就像剛剛 是他下班時間 會跟我報備 \n突然有種 啊 再也不會出現了的念頭 \n然後眼淚就自己流下來 真麻煩啊 失戀\n沒什麼 只是想說 也許有人現在也跟我一樣吧哈哈\n\n然後我用了之前創一人群組的辦法\n假裝他還在的和他對話\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/010d6cae-82f4-453e-b32b-416142283d53/1280.jpeg\n感覺有點變態🤣🤣🤣\n但是沒辦法 我想他 想得不得了\n我怕我會忍不住聯繫他\n說到這 眼淚又自己留下來了 真麻煩啊 失戀","excerpt":"如題 昨天分手了 我提的，我喜歡對方 但感覺對方不喜歡了 所以成全他，最後提完 對方已讀不回後 就邁入失戀階段了，以前也失戀過 只能靠時間治癒，可能是太有經驗 比較不會像以前哭到無法下床，或是半夜無法","anonymousSchool":true,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"42851318-b9e2-4a75-8a05-9fe180becefe","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-28T15:20:13.196Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-28T15:20:13.196Z","commentCount":253,"likeCount":3626,"tags":[],"topics":["分手","失戀","感情","前男友"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"感情","forumAlias":"relationship","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":3381},{"id":"514c2569-fd53-4d9d-a415-bf0f88e7329f","count":222},{"id":"e8e6bc5d-41b0-4129-b134-97507523d7ff","count":17},{"id":"011ead16-9b83-4729-9fde-c588920c6c2d","count":3},{"id":"4b018f48-e184-445f-adf1-fc8e04ba09b9","count":3}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/010d6cae-82f4-453e-b32b-416142283d53/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"c247220b-6662-4d42-af8a-556ec52a4e83","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/010d6cae-82f4-453e-b32b-416142283d53/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/010d6cae-82f4-453e-b32b-416142283d53/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/010d6cae-82f4-453e-b32b-416142283d53/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOT